  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t知乎提问，如何看待一地建立外卖配送行业党委，一个回答很有意思。而评论区也各种附和。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n虽然也有人说，这种党委其实没有多大权力，也没福利。但人们也不关心具体怎么回事了，就是乐。“塔西佗陷阱”下，党、政府，公信力都没有了，所以即便没有滥用权力，大家也不信了。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n虽然这种“团建”也没啥用，但是也是一种解构和发泄。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2E2Mjk2ZTQ4N2FmNTQ0ZTkyMTkzLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7a6296e487af544e92193.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7a6296e487af544e92193.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7a6296e487af544e92193.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGQ3NDI0YmQ3YTNkOTE3NWQ4YzA0LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd7424bd7a3d9175d8c04.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd7424bd7a3d9175d8c04.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dd7424bd7a3d9175d8c04.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvY2EzZWY2ODA3MDNiYmIwYzBiOWE0LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca3ef680703bbb0c0b9a4.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca3ef680703bbb0c0b9a4.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ca3ef680703bbb0c0b9a4.png?width=750&amp;height=1334\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWE0ZTlmNDY2Mzk1Nzc4NjdmMjA1LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEzMzQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ea4e9f46639